  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110128531701\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110128531701\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \r\n<p>치료받으러 내원하시는 환자분들의 가족입니다.</p>\r\n<p>아이들은 기다리는시간을 제일 지루해하죠^^ 병원이라&nbsp;장난감도 마땅치 않구요..</p>\r\n<p>심심해하길래 \"사진놀이 할사라~~~암\" 했더니 서로 하겠다고 해서 카메라에 담아줬습니다^^</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/79fe1f89cf8b4590.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"412\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 550px; rheight: 412px\" id=\"20120109_69/isuhani_1326087208132lL1OX_JPEG/P1063023.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A42C08F5')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/79fe1f89cf8b4590.jpg\"></p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" />* 참고로 두 아이는 이날 처음만난 사이랍니다^^ 아이들의 친화력은 대단한 것 같아요*</p>\r\n<p>이번에는 서로 찍어주겠다고 해서 카메라를 빌려줬습니다</p>\r\n<p>사진작가 해도 될만큼 너무너무 잘 찍어줬네요^^</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20120109_282/isuhani_13260871017866nmX6_JPEG/P1063024.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"412\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 550px; rheight: 412px\" id=\"20120109_282/isuhani_13260871017866nmX6_JPEG/P1063024.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A42C08F5')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20120109_282/isuhani_13260871017866nmX6_JPEG/P1063024.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20120109_17/isuhani_1326087102097yyolW_JPEG/P1063025.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"412\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 550px; rheight: 412px\" id=\"20120109_17/isuhani_1326087102097yyolW_JPEG/P1063025.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A42C08F5')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20120109_17/isuhani_1326087102097yyolW_JPEG/P1063025.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20120109_25/isuhani_1326087102427vndE9_JPEG/P1063026.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"412\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 550px; rheight: 412px\" id=\"20120109_25/isuhani_1326087102427vndE9_JPEG/P1063026.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A42C08F5')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20120109_25/isuhani_1326087102427vndE9_JPEG/P1063026.JPG?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>마지막 사진은 &nbsp;모델 뺨치죠??</p>\r\n<p>아이들 덕분에 미소짓는 하루를 보낼 수 있었습니다^^ </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
